data.description:
Country living at its best. Relax on the back deck while watching the sunset. 3 bedrooms, 3 baths with bonus room and two-car garage. Well-maintained with lots of upgrades; new roof in 2021. You don’t want to miss this one!
Conveniently located to amenities: 10mins from Moss Lake, Woodbridge Golf Course and new casino; 30 mins to CLT airport; 45 mins to Charlotte.
